  "title": "[FAST HIRE!] Technical Services Technician | Up to $2.5k + Allowances | 3/4 Day Week",
  "description": "<p>💰Salary:  Up to $2500 + $334 (Night Shift Allowance) + $70 (Meal) + $70 (Transport)</p><p>📍Location: Jurong East</p><p><strong>Shift Pattern & Working Hours:</strong><br />🕒12-Hour Shift\n(4-3-3-4 Work Cycle)</p><ul><li>Work 4 days → Rest 3 days</li><li>Following week Work 3 days → Rest 4 days</li><li>Cycle repeats</li></ul><p>🌙Fixed Shift: Sunday Night Shift</p><p>Start: 7:45 PM → End: 7:55 AM</p><p>Key Responsibilities</p><ul><li>Operate manufacturing equipment to meet production schedules and output targets</li><li>Provide technical troubleshooting support to minimize downtime and ensure quality standards</li><li>Perform daily and monthly preventive maintenance activities</li><li>Participate in safety initiatives, quality improvement projects, and continuous improvement programs</li><li>Maintain proper documentation and adhere strictly to SOPs and safety regulations</li></ul><p>Requirements</p><ul><li>Minimum NITEC in Engineering discipline (Preferably Mechanical / Mechatronics / Robotics / Electrical)</li><li>Ability to read and understand mechanical & electrical diagrams</li><li>Willing to perform 12-hour rotating shifts and overtime when required</li><li>Open to fresh graduates</li><li>Singaporeans only</li></ul><p>📩 Interested? Apply Now!</p><p>Send your resume in to: admin@crew.sg<br /><br />For a quicker reply, text us at: 91728913 or 88914996</p><p>Please include your availability, notice period, and expected salary.</p><p>* Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Branson Yong</p><p>Outsourcing Team</p><p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet</p><p>EA 24C2435</p>",
